    >
    <p
      ><strong>PARTNERS</strong>:
      <span class="font-serif"
        >Mural Arts Institute, City of Philadelphia Department of Behavioral
        Health and Intellectual disAbility Services, Health Federation of
        Philadelphia, European Institute of Public Health Policy in
        Ukraine.</span
      ></p
    >
    <p class="font-serif"
      >The study tour and visit to Philadelphia were made possible by the
      support of the Health Federation of Philadelphia and in collaboration with
      the USAID Public Health System Recovery and Resilience Activity (PHS R&R)
      led by Pact.</p
